reviews.review_text:
Cool Kiel Auditorium link~ As I listen to these great snippets from GD history, I also like to 'google' the old venues, to look for pics of and from inside of them; here's a cool photo album of the Kiel Auditorium.
Great AUD here, btw.  God bless the tapers, and God bless the good ol' Grateful Dead!
